Interface VoteRepository

    @Repository
public interface VoteRepository
extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<Vote,java.lang.Long>

        Vote findByUserAndRecipe(User user,

        This method finds in Vote database table records with user and recipe fields equal to ones provided as a parameters of this method and returns it as a Vote object.
